OL,3,CAlcohol deaths drop by more than 20%
OL,4,Cin Dumfries and Galloway
OL,6,FAlcohol deaths in 2024 across Dumfries
OL,7,Fand Galloway have dropped by more than
OL,8,F20% compared to 2023, National Record
OL,9,Fof Scotland statistics show.
OL,11,FThere were 25 alcohol specific deaths
OL,12,Fin the region in 2024, a drop of seven
OL,13,Fcompared to the 32 deaths recorded in
OL,14,F2023.
OL,16,FThe Scottish Borders also saw a
OL,17,Freduction in the level of alcohol
OL,18,Fdeaths, with a drop of 9.1% in 2024
OL,19,Fcompared to 2023.
