OL,3,CAlcohol deaths drop by more than 20%
OL,4,Cin Dumfries and Galloway
OL,6,FIn the Scottish Borders there were 20
OL,7,Fdeaths in 2024 compared to 22 the
OL,8,Fprevious year.
OL,10,FNationally the number of alcohol
OL,11,Frelated deaths in Scotland are at
OL,12,Ftheir lowest level since 2019 and saw
OL,13,Fa seven percent reduction in 2024
OL,14,Fcompared to 2023.
OL,16,FPhillipa Haxton, Head of Vital Events
OL,17,FStatistics, said: "The number of
OL,18,Falcohol-specific deaths decreased by
OL,19,F7% in 2024 compared with the previous
OL,20,Fyear. This is the lowest figure since
OL,21,F2019, before the pandemic.
