OL,3,CAlcohol deaths drop by more than 20%
OL,4,Cin Dumfries and Galloway
OL,6,F"The average age at death has risen
OL,7,Fover the last decade and is now 60
OL,8,Fyears for males and 58 for females."
OL,10,FAcross the whole of Scotland there
OL,11,Fwere 1,185 alcohol deaths in 2024, a
OL,12,Freduction of 92 compared to 2023.
OL,14,FScottish Drugs and Alcohol Policy
OL,15,FMinister Maree Todd said: "Behind
OL,16,Fevery number is a person and my
OL,17,Fheartfelt condolences go out to those
OL,18,Faffected by the loss of a loved one
OL,19,Fthrough alcohol.
