OL,4,Cin Dumfries and Galloway
OL,6,F"This is a public health priority and
OL,7,Fwe are continuing to channel our
OL,8,Fenergy towards reducing alcohol harm
OL,9,Ffurther. There is still a lot of work
OL,10,Fto be done to save and improve lives."
OL,12,FCompared to the rest of the UK,
OL,13,FScotland is still at the top of the
OL,14,Fcharts when it comes to alcohol deaths
OL,15,Ffor 2024.
OL,17,FThe country is higher than both the UK
OL,18,Fnational average and compared to the
OL,19,Fother nations in the UK.
